reviewText: I was happy with this product

Unwinding, shedding fears and woes. Visual and audio therapy to de-stress! That's what this dose of peaceful rendezvous will do for you. Soul therapy to touch the inner places of your being. This is what this visual journey with music does for me. I am now seeking out more of these videos, as I am wearing out this one! ts a mind liberating spell I so need in  life reminding me its the calm that keeps me mentally healthy.
